13 (i) In the event a unit owner sustains damage to the owner’s unit as a result of an event that
14 is covered under the insurance coverage purchased in accordance with this section, then upon
15 written request to the condominium association, the unit owner shall be entitled to a written copy
16 from the condominium association of the insurance company damage appraisal or any damage
17 appraisal in regard to damage to the owner’s unit, within fourteen (14) calendar days of the date of
18 the unit owner’s request, or within fourteen (14) days of the association’s receipt of the damage
